Amiantit Unit Sells Amitech South Africa Stake for $2.1 Million

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-03-05T07:40:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-05/amiantit-unit-sells-amitech-south-africa-stake-for-2-1-million.html
  Saudi Arabian Amiantit Co. (SAAC) , a
producer of building materials, said its Amitech Switzerland
unit sold its stake in  Amitech South Africa  for 7.9 million
riyals ($2.1 million), Amiantit said in a statement to the  Saudi
bourse website .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
